    Tableau tabcmd Released for beta

    Posted on 31 January 2022

    The tabcmd command-line utility version 2.0 is now available for beta users

    On January 31st, we moved the latest version of the tabcmd command-line utility to version 2.0. This version supports multifactor authentication and allows you to use the utility from remote machines.

    We also made this a GitHub project. This means that you can contribute to the code. To install and use tabcmd, download from the GitHub project.

This site is open source. Suggestions and pull requests are welcome on our GitHub page.
